|MKOThis command allows you to pick up items without anyone else
knowing you picked them up.  It costs a mere 20sp, and works
exactly like "get" or "take". Also can use the "palm all". 
A Thief must always be the master of deception, so quickly 
palm that item and don't let others see you've picked it up. 


|CKOGLVL required: |GKB4
|CKOSyntax: |YKOpalm <item/all>               |CKOCost: |WKO10
